title: More with Rumors Donkey of the Day, Ask Yee
itunes:title: More with Rumors Donkey of the Day, Ask Yee
description:
For the next portion of the podcast Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to a  Doctor after giving a VASECTOMY to a 4 year old during surgery to treat a hernia in his groin. Also, Angela gave some celebrity tea during the rumors and helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee" where a listener needed help with getting a raise at her job. 

 

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
